Description:Tests the Clone mechanic via Copy Artifact (mtg-566). P0 has Copy Artifact in hand and enough mana (3 Islands) to cast it. P1 controls a Black Lotus (an artifact). When Copy Artifact resolves, its ETBReplacement:Copy/DB$ Clone effect must prompt P0 to choose an artifact to copy, then enter the battlefield as a copy of Black Lotus that is ALSO an Enchantment (AddTypes$ Enchantment, CR 707).

